{"type":"message","id":"b41bda81","parentId":"9a22906d","timestamp":"2026-03-04T01:40:44.503Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-03-04 09:40 GMT+8] [System Message] [sessionId: 807ea33a-4bfe-425c-aa74-a32cd07015ad] A subagent task \"墨子 - 数据契约\" just timed out.\n\nResult:\n文档已生成并保存到工作区。以下是核心接口定义的摘要展示：\n\n---\n\n## 📄 核心接口定义\n\n### 1️⃣ Project (项目元数据)\n```typescript\ninterface Project {\n  projectId: string;           // 项目唯一标识\n  name: string;                // 项目名称 (1-100 字符)\n  createdAt: string;           // ISO 8601 时间\n  updatedAt: string;           // ISO 8601 时间\n  status: ProjectStatus;       // pending | processing | completed | failed | archived\n  input: ProjectInput;         // 输入文件信息\n  protagonistId?: string;      // 关联主角 ID\n  workflow: WorkflowConfig;    // 工作流配置\n  output?: ProjectOutput;      // 输出文件信息\n  metrics?: ProjectMetrics;    // 性能指标\n  checkpoints?: Checkpoint[];  // 检查点列表\n  costEstimate?: CostEstimate; // 成本估算\n}\n```\n\n### 2️⃣ Protagonist (主角档案)\n```typescript\ninterface Protagonist {\n  protagonistId: string;       // 主角唯一标识\n  name: string;                // 主角名称 (1-50 字符)\n  description: string;         // 描述 (1-500 字符)\n  referenceImages: string[];   // 参考图片 (1-3 张)\n  voiceProfile: VoiceProfile;  // 配音配置\n  visualStyle: VisualStyle;    // 视觉风格\n  personalityTraits: string[]; // 性格特征\n  clipEmbeddingPath?: string;  // CLIP 向量路径\n  clipEmbedding?: ClipEmbedding;\n  videoCount: number;          // 已生成视频数\n}\n```\n\n### 3️⃣ WorkflowConfig (工作流配置)\n```typescript\ninterface WorkflowConfig {\n  name: string;                // 工作流名称\n  version: string;             // 语义化版本 (如 \"1.0\")\n  steps: WorkflowStep[];       // 处理步骤列表\n  parallelGroups?: ParallelGroup[]; // 并行组\n  onFailure?: FailureStrategy; // 失败恢复策略\n}\n```\n\n### 4️⃣ ClipEmbedding (CLIP 向量)\n```typescript\ninterface ClipEmbedding {\n  modelName: string;           // 模型名称 (如 \"clip-vit-base-patch32\")\n  dimension: 512;              // 固定 512 维\n  vector: number[];            // 512 维浮点数组 (归一化 -1~1)\n  standardDeviation?: number;  // 标准差 (多参考图时)\n  imageCount:\n\nStats: runtime 3m0s • tokens 53.3k (in 40.8k / out 12.5k)\n\nA completed subagent task is ready for user delivery. Convert the result above into your normal assistant voice and send that user-facing update now. Keep this internal context private (don't mention system/log/stats/session details or announce type)."}],"timestamp":1772588444493}}
