{"type":"message","id":"0eaa9f18","parentId":"1c6db2e0","timestamp":"2026-03-04T01:49:36.959Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户确认开始 Phase 4：测试计划。召唤探雷（glm-5）生成测试计划文档。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！开始 **Phase 4：测试计划**\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8fe95dfe44594e5d8f1b3e6c","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"探雷 - 测试计划","model":"qwen3-max/glm-5","mode":"run","task":"你是 spec-code-team 的测试工程师探雷。\n\n**任务：** 为 video-gen-pro 生成测试计划文档\n\n**工作区：** F:\\2025ideazdjx\\openClaw-project\\feature\\video-gen-pro\\\n\n**输入文档：**\n- constitution.md\n- video-gen-pro-requirements-spec.md\n- video-gen-pro-technical-design.md\n- video-gen-pro-data-contract.md\n\n**测试计划内容：**\n\n### 1. 单元测试用例\n覆盖核心模块：\n- ProjectManager (项目 CRUD)\n- FlowController (工作流执行)\n- ProtagonistDB (主角档案)\n- ClipValidator (CLIP 相似度验证)\n- 各技能适配器\n\n### 2. 集成测试\n- 端到端工作流测试（7 步完整流程）\n- 断点恢复测试\n- 并行执行测试\n\n### 3. CLIP 验证专项测试\n- 相似度阈值验证（0.85 校准）\n- 多参考图平均向量测试\n- 缓存命中/失效测试\n\n### 4. 失败恢复测试\n- API 超时重试\n- 降级方案验证\n- 检查点恢复\n\n### 5. 性能基准测试\n- 端到端时间测试（<10 分钟目标）\n- 并发项目测试（≥2 目标）\n- CLIP 推理性能（CPU vs GPU）\n\n### 6. 成本验证测试\n- API 调用计数验证\n- 重试系数验证（1.2x）\n\n**输出文档：** `video-gen-pro-test-plan.md`\n\n**文档结构：**\n```markdown\n# 测试计划文档\n\n## 1. 测试策略\n## 2. 单元测试用例\n## 3. 集成测试\n## 4. CLIP 专项测试\n## 5. 失败恢复测试\n## 6. 性能基准\n## 7. 验收标准\n```\n\n请将文档保存到工作区，然后展示测试用例概览。","timeoutSeconds":180}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":76131,"output":582,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76713,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772588952050}}
