{"type":"message","id":"84216676","parentId":"92acce5e","timestamp":"2026-03-04T03:38:58.252Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要完整的安装、配置、启动命令，我一步步给出来。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！给你完整的 **安装 → 配置 → 启动** 一条龙命令：\n\n---\n\n## 📦 1. 安装 LiteLLM\n\n```bash\npip install 'litellm[proxy]'\n```\n\n**验证安装：**\n```bash\nlitellm --version\n```\n\n---\n\n## ⚙️ 2. 创建配置文件\n\n```bash\n# 创建工作目录\nmkdir C:\\litellm-proxy\ncd C:\\litellm-proxy\n\n# 创建配置文件\nnotepad config.yaml\n```\n\n**粘贴以下内容：**\n```yaml\nmodel_list:\n  # 通义千问\n  - model_name: qwen3.5-plus\n    litellm_params:\n      model: openai/qwen3.5-plus\n      api_base: https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1\n      api_key: os.environ/QWEN_API_KEY\n\n  # Kimi\n  - model_name: kimi-k2.5\n    litellm_params:\n      model: openai/kimi-k2.5\n      api_base: https://api.moonshot.cn/v1\n      api_key: os.environ/KIMI_API_KEY\n\n  # 智谱 GLM\n  - model_name: glm-5\n    litellm_params:\n      model: openai/glm-5\n      api_base: https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4\n      api_key: os.environ/ZHIPU_API_KEY\n\n  # Qwen-Coder\n  - model_name: qwen-coder-plus\n    litellm_params:\n      model: openai/qwen3-coder-plus\n      api_base: https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1\n      api_key: os.environ/QWEN_API_KEY\n\n  # Qwen-Max\n  - model_name: qwen3-max\n    litellm_params:\n      model: openai/qwen3-max-2026-01-23\n      api_base: https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1\n      api_key: os.environ/QWEN_API_KEY\n\n# 通用设置\ngeneral_settings:\n  master_key: sk-litellm-1234  # 可选，保护代理\n```\n\n保存关闭。\n\n---\n\n## 🔑 3. 设置环境变量\n\n**临时设置（当前会话）：**\n```bash\n$env:QWEN_API_KEY=\"你的阿里云 Key\"\n$env:KIMI_API_KEY=\"你的 Moonshot Key\"\n$env:ZHIPU_API_KEY=\"你的智谱 Key\"\n```\n\n**永久设置（推荐）：**\n```bash\n[Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\"QWEN_API_KEY\", \"你的阿里云 Key\", \"User\")\n[Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\"KIMI_API_KEY\", \"你的 Moonshot Key\", \"User\")\n[Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\"ZHIPU_API_KEY\", \"你的智谱 Key\", \"User\")\n\n# 刷新当前会话\nrefreshenv\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 4. 启动 LiteLLM\n\n### 方式 A：前台运行（开发测试）\n```bash\ncd C:\\litellm-proxy\nlitellm --config config.yaml --port 3000\n```\n\n**停止：** `Ctrl + C`\n\n---\n\n### 方式 B：后台运行（长期使用）\n```bash\ncd C:\\litellm-proxy\nStart-Process python -ArgumentList \"-m\",\"litellm\",\"--config\",\"config.yaml\",\"--port\",\"3000\" -WindowStyle Hidden\n```\n\n**停止：**\n```bash\nStop-Process -Name python -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n```\n\n---\n\n### 方式 C：创建批处理脚本（推荐）\n\n**创建 `start.bat`：**\n```bash\nnotepad C:\\litellm-proxy\\start.bat\n```\n\n**粘贴：**\n```batch\n@echo off\necho Starting LiteLLM Proxy...\ncd /d %~dp0\nstart \"LiteLLM Proxy\" cmd /k \"litellm --config config.yaml --port 3000\"\necho LiteLLM started in new window.\necho Press any key to exit this window...\npause >nul\n```\n\n**创建 `stop.bat`：**\n```bash\nnotepad C:\\litellm-proxy\\stop.bat\n```\n\n**粘贴：**\n```batch\n@echo off\necho Stopping LiteLLM Proxy...\ntaskkill /F /FI \"WINDOWTITLE eq LiteLLM Proxy*\"\necho LiteLLM stopped.\npause\n```\n\n**使用：**\n```bash\n# 启动\nC:\\litellm-proxy\\start.bat\n\n# 停止\nC:\\litellm-proxy\\stop.bat\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 5. 测试是否工作\n\n```bash\n# 检查健康状态\ncurl http://localhost:3000/health\n\n# 查看支持的模型\ncurl http://localhost:3000/v1/models\n\n# 测试 Qwen 调用\ncurl http://localhost:3000/v1/chat/completions -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d \"{\\\"model\\\":\\\"qwen3.5-plus\\\",\\\"messages\\\":[{\\\"role\\\":\\\"user\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"你好\\\"}]}\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 6. 配置 Codex 使用代理\n\n```bash\nnotepad C:\\Users\\14015\\.codex\\config.toml\n```\n\n**修改/添加：**\n```toml\n[model_providers.local]\nname = \"LiteLLM Proxy\"\nbase_url = \"http://localhost:3000\"\nwire_api = \"responses\"\nenv_key = \"DUMMY\"\n\n[profiles.qwen3.5-plus]\nmodel = \"qwen3.5-plus\"\nmodel_provider = \"local\"\napproval_policy = \"on-request\"\nsandbox_mode = \"read-only\"\n```\n\n**测试 Codex：**\n```bash\ncodex '你好，测试 LiteLLM 代理'\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 完整命令汇总\n\n```bash\n# ========== 安装 ==========\npip install 'litellm[proxy]'\n\n# ========== 创建目录 ==========\nmkdir C:\\litellm-proxy\ncd C:\\litellm-proxy\n\n# ========== 设置环境变量 ==========\n[Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\"QWEN_API_KEY\", \"你的 Key\", \"User\")\nrefreshenv\n\n# ========== 启动 ==========\nlitellm --config config.yaml --port 3000\n\n# ========== 测试 ==========\ncurl http://localhost:3000/health\ncurl http://localhost:3000/v1/models\n\n# ========== Codex 测试 ==========\ncodex '你好'\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 一键启动脚本（终极版）\n\n**创建 `run.ps1`：**\n```powershell\n# C:\\litellm-proxy\\run.ps1\n$env:QWEN_API_KEY = \"你的 Key\"\n$env:KIMI_API_KEY = \"你的 Key\"\n\nWrite-Host \"Starting LiteLLM Proxy on http://localhost:3000\" -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"Press Ctrl+C to stop\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n\nlitellm --config config.yaml --port 3000\n```\n\n**运行：**\n```bash\nC:\\litellm-proxy\\run.ps1\n```\n\n---\n\n**老板，直接复制粘贴执行就行！有问题随时喊我！** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":113051,"output":1662,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114713,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772595460512}}
