{"type":"message","id":"232c8848","parentId":"1a75fd1b","timestamp":"2026-03-04T06:43:29.786Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"创建启动脚本 start.bat","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a0a944e2332547baa3ce4aa7","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"@echo off\nchcp 65001 >nul\necho.\necho ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\necho ║              Qwen Proxy Server v1.0.0                    ║\necho ║     OpenAI Responses API → Chat Completions Proxy        ║\necho ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\necho.\n\ncd /d %~dp0\n\nREM 加载环境变量\nif exist .env (\n    echo [✓] 加载配置文件 .env\n    for /f \"delims=\" %%a in ('findstr /v \"^#\" .env ^| findstr /v \"^$\"') do (\n        set %%a\n    )\n) else (\n    echo [✗] 未找到 .env 文件，使用系统环境变量\n)\n\nREM 检查 QWEN_API_KEY\nif \"%QWEN_API_KEY%\"==\"\" (\n    echo.\n    echo [⚠ 警告] QWEN_API_KEY 未设置！\n    echo 请编辑 .env 文件或设置系统环境变量\n    echo.\n)\n\necho.\necho [✓] 启动 Qwen Proxy 服务器\necho [✓] 监听端口：http://localhost:3000\necho [✓] 可用端点:\necho       - POST /v1/responses (Responses API)\necho       - POST /v1/chat/completions (Chat API)\necho       - GET  /v1/models\necho       - GET  /health\necho.\necho 按 Ctrl+C 停止服务\necho.\n\npython proxy.py\n\npause\n","path":"C:\\qwen-proxy\\start.bat"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":177821,"output":420,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":178241,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772606602167}}
